params.buyerSettlementAddress: Address of the settlement which bought workers

calculateProsperityForExactWorkers(uint2.details: Returns valid output only for integer workersToBuy value (in 1e0 precision)

returns._0: Amount of prosperity needed for workersToBuy

era().details: Value is dereferenced from proxy storage and world

params.initParams: Encoded init params (every world asset has own knowledge how to extract data from it)

swapProsperityForExactWorkers(address,ui.details: Even though function is opened, it can only be called by world asset

params.maxProsperityToSell: Maximum amount of prosperity to be taken for exact amount of workers

returns._0: Amount of workers bought by prosperity

world().details: Value is dereferenced from proxy storage

lastPurchaseTime.details: Updated every time when #swapProsperityForExactWorkers is called

relatedRegion.details: Immutable, initialized on the region creation

workerPrice.details: Updated every time when #swapProsperityForExactWorkers is called

CannotHireWorkersDueToNotEnoughProsperit.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire workers due to not having enough prosperity in settlement for the purchase

CannotHireWorkersDueToTheirCostIsHigherT.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire worker due to their cost is being higher than max prosperity to sell specified

CannotHireWorkersExceedingTransactionLim.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire more workers than transaction limit

CannotHireWorkersInvalidWorkersToBuySpec.notice: Thrown when attempting to hire workers with invalid workers to buy specified

OnlyActiveGame().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called in active game (started and not finished)

OnlyMightyCreator().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by mighty creator

OnlyWorldAssetFromSameEra().notice: Thrown when attempting to call action which can only be called by world asset from same era

calculateProsperityForExactWorkers(uint2.notice: Calculates input of prosperity based on output whole amount of workers

lastPurchaseTime().notice: Time at which last purchase is performed

relatedRegion().notice: Region to which this pool belongs

worldAssetFactory().notice: Returns world asset factory from registry
